## Core features:

- ✅ Byte output format
- ✅ Assembly output format
- ✅ String extraction (ASCII and Unicode)
- ✅ Hex dump output

## File format support:

Detection executables file and parsing and analysis for:
- ✅Executable files:  PE, ELF, Mach-O, Java class files, Android DEX, WebAssembly
- ✅ Documents: PDF, DOCX, PPTX detection
- ✅ Compressed - ZIP, TAR, APK
- ✅ Scripts: PowerShell, Python, JavaScript detection with security analysis
- Firmware: Intel HEX, Motorola S-record, raw firmware analysis



## Enhanced CLI interface:

- ✅ Multiple output format options (-f byte|assembly|strings|hex|all)
- ✅ File type forcing (-t raw|pe|elf|apk|pdf|zip|tar)
- ✅ Interactive mode (-i)
- ✅ Verbose analysis (-v)


## Advanced Malware Detection

- Crypter Recognition: Detect encrypted/encoded payloads
- Anti-Analysis Techniques: Find anti-debugging, anti-VM, sandbox evasion
- Polymorphic Code Detection: Identify self-modifying code patterns
- ✅ PACKER DETECTION: UPX, ASPack, Themida, VMProtect detection
- ✅ Heuristic analysis with entropy calculation
- ✅ Generic packer detection patterns
- ✅ Confidence scoring and unpacking recommendations
- Control Flow Flattening: Unravel obfuscated code
- String Decryption: Runtime string analysis
- Dead Code Elimination: Clean up analysis


## Multi-Architecture Support

- ARM/ARM64: Mobile malware, IoT devices
- MIPS: Router/embedded device analysis
- PowerPC: Legacy systems
- RISC-V: Emerging architecture support

## Advanced Vulnerability Classes

- Use-After-Free: Memory corruption patterns
- Double-Free: Heap corruption detection
- Race Conditions: Threading vulnerability patterns
- SQL Injection: Pattern recognition in binaries
- XXE/SSRF: Web service vulnerability patterns


## Dynamic Analysis Integration

- Execution Tracing: Step-through debugging
- Memory Monitoring: Heap/stack state tracking
- System Call Monitoring: API call analysis
- Network Behavior: Communication pattern analysis


## Machine Learning Enhancement

- Behavioral Classification: ML-based threat categorization
- Anomaly Detection: Statistical analysis of code patterns
- Signature Generation: Auto-generate YARA rules
- False Positive Reduction: Smart filtering

## Visualization & Reporting

- Control Flow Graphs: Visual representation
- Call Graphs: Function relationship mapping
- Heat Maps: Vulnerability density visualization
- Export Formats: JSON, XML, CSV, SARIF

