- Plugin System: Extensible architecture
- API Interface: REST API for automation
- Database Backend: Store analysis results
- SIEM Integration: Export to security platforms

## Performance & Scalability

- Parallel Processing: Multi-threaded analysis
- Streaming Analysis: Large file handling
- Caching System: Speed up repeated analysis
- Distributed Processing: Cloud-scale analysis


